    "C Method for adding lensing template (LT) as an independent channelIn this method, we treat the lensing template as an additional pseudo-channel, instead of doing any delensing process on the map level, then calculate the auto and cross power spectra to form the theoretical model vector.",
    "Our map channels will be [B obs, B LT], then the dataset vector can be Xℓ where parameter A L scales the amplitude of the reconstructed lensing B-mode.",
    "The covariance matrix of Xℓ is estimated from 500 signal+noise simulations to capture all the complexities.",
    "D Contribution of Tensor and Scalar componentsWe check the contribution of the polarization modes induced by the tensor and scalar fluctuation to the delensing results by simulation.",
    "The input maps share the same seed, and we adopt the current upper limit for r, which is r = 0.036."
